            "heading": "The Guarantee",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_GeV3tJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Now we know that this still leaves you to make a massive leap of faith. But remember that this is a completely non-invasive treatment that requires you sleeping with an appliance in your mouth.<br\/><br\/><strong>It costs just $100<\/strong>, and we fully refund your money within 90 days if after making a consistent effort you decide it is not working for you. To demonstrate this we ask that you try to sleep with the appliance for a period of 30 days.<br\/><br\/>Note that the guarantee only applies when purchasing the support package.  If you buy just the appliance there is no guarantee as it is a 'do-it-yourself' approach.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        }
      },
